hopobject.body: I can't get a signal muscle fibre selection This was a day when it was thought the old man would not make it through the day. So there had been this steady procession of people, to stand here and take pictures, and once again take full measure of what Mandela did and what he meant and how he reminded us, as much as any figure in this century or the last one or the one before that, how one man really can still change the world.
